Installation:
--
Place the "maps" folder inside your cstrike directory. Usually located at
C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\"account name"\counter-strike source\cstrike

Comments:
--
This is the first release of this map, and I am looking at creating a second one sometime in the next few weeks. Basically I am releasing this version in order to gain public opinion, and see what others would like to have added to the map.
